headline: Warren Buffett’s New Stock Bets Revealed — Should You Buy In, Too?
summary: Recently, Warren Buffett’s holding company, Berkshire Hathaway, filed its quarterly Form 13F equity investment portfolio, providing investors with an update regarding the company’s holdings. The filing indicated, among other things, five newer holdings that Buffett and Berkshire have acquired, including one rather surprising investment in a very controversial and embattled company.
